    "body": "For (2) I don't think it's nearly that simple. `state.finalized_slot` being updated depends not just on the pattern of justified slots but also on what the `state.previous_justified_slot` was at the time it was updated. So I don't think we can get rid of `finalized_slot`. We also need `state.previous_justified_slot` and `state.justified_slot` to remember what was the `source` that messages were supposed to be using in the previous two epochs, and that's not something that can necessarily be figured out from a justification bitfield because the justification bitfield might change but the justification sources should not change.",
